{"tid":1145161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國軟件公司大規模裁減中國員","createTime":"2019-05-08T13:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T09:33:09.000Z","uid":1251,"like":277,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b8f196dbf5cc3a07611c02a2179e0026fa92b9","tid":1145161,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:34:00.000Z","msg":"【有線中國組：美國軟件公司大規模裁減中國員工】<br />\n<br />\n來自美國的全球第二大軟件公司甲骨文，宣布大規模裁減中國研發中心的員工。估計被裁減人數近千人，有受影響既員工表示，今次裁員沒有任何先兆，懷疑背後涉及政治因素，和中美技術之爭有關。<br />\n<br />\n留意稍後《有線中國組》節目，會有詳細報道。<br />\n <br />\n今晚 9:30 凌晨 00:30 有線新聞台<br />\n <br />\n#有線新聞‬　有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1106071096251624?s=764338867&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1106071096251624%3Fs%3D764338867%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=0c2c7188\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1106071096251624?s=764338867&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"d7d2cfef6ded852b0f7d0fbbf33afab384e33d5b","tid":1145161,"uid":1251,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國又贏"},{"pid":"814015feb590a755f830984e3893a922a1b9b1d5","tid":1145161,"uid":3340,"like":119,"dislike":2,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"明正言順帶技術返終國，贏到開巷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095abbc9007cc4cd6aee0022002834364ce4de39","tid":1145161,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6213930e1a93b148729ff6dbaaec993f6879ced","tid":1145161,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quot